OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fwill die away during this evening.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,8,Fbut clouding over during the early
OL,9,Fhours, perhaps a little rain in the
OL,10,Ffar south later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA cloudy day to come with
OL,13,Foccasional rain spreading north.
OL,14,FBecoming drier later in the afternoon.
OL,15,FHeavier rain extending northeast in
OL,16,Fthe evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
