OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FBands
OL,6,Fof rain, some heavy, push northeast
OL,7,Fwith showers, some heavy and thundery,
OL,8,Ffollowing Wednesday afternoon. These
OL,9,Fshowers clear overnight into Thursday.
OL,10,FA further rain band pushes northeast
OL,11,FFriday.
